{{Quote|Ken's one of the brightest students at a very special school, Dagobah Tech. At the moment he's on vacation. Ken's classmates are the sons and daughters of the scientists who work at DRAPAC, our fortress, on Mount Yoda on the planet Dagobah.|Luke Skywalker|<ref name="Prophets of the Dark Side (novel)">[[Prophets of the Dark Side (novel)|''Prophets of the Dark Side'']]</ref>}}
'''Dagobah Tech''' was a school established by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] near [[Mount Yoda]] in [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]].

